Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流行性？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳下腺炎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱作  流行性耳下腺炎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是常說的多福感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要休養一個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打針呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The spear is very break and hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it is large and long,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jurinsa thows it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahunture grabs it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As she pressing it against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she had never fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到學美出院為止  學生會就只剩我和芽生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這些都要…整理啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說來  還從沒跟小芽單獨說過話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力和小芽愉快地聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後回家的時候再一起吃個飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:02.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾衣竿  賣晾衣竿了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒法辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得學美一不在就沒人起頭聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是神經太過緊繃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不好意思  明天壘球部還有體能訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是跟你談這些的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  只要適當地配合一下她的話題不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣的話題才算？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看過的電視之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽好像不看電視的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近聽過的CD呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像喜歡聽古典的  我一點都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來她會笑話我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  找人幫忙的話去找小桃啊  去找小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經叫她了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道小芽就是這性格  跟她妥協一下也沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才剛進的學生會  心裡比你還沒底呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好對人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  囉哩吧嗦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  吃飯吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜…柑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（關門  請明天再來）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我今天有事不能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊…是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  跟她交上朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問到甚麼隱私了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都在聊些甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭宣傳時的CG真的是衛藤同學做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說  跟她單獨在一起一定很吃力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她心裡比你還沒底呢  好好對人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要好好對她的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然  雖然用嘴說不上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要寫信  能有個開端的話  肯定能跟她拉近距離
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能成為好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要踏出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個  還真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你常來這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒來過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏出第一步  踏出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫給誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  給學美寫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光香  早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想去學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要遲到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  我今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了對了  有你的信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有郵戳  應該是直接放在郵箱裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就吃麵包吧  沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  光香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話給上原同學商量了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她建議我要不要寫寫信看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就寫了這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…其實我並不擅長跟人交談
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不是不想交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道該怎麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為甚麼昨天沒接電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道該怎麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻森同學你既溫柔  又開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要是能與你自由地交談該多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會  要一起加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「給稻森同學  衛藤芽生」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一部分同學對學園祭是否會延期有所疑問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事哦  學園祭的準備活動才剛剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會延期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會還有蜜柑和小芽在  大概沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你們這身衣服在哪裡買的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主題？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯  在上次的學生總會上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所要展現的學園祭的大致概念  我們已經能瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  具體來說\N你們到底想要得到甚麼效果  該如何行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不事先定好方針的話  或許也會和去年一樣搞出個不知所謂的學園祭來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  「生機勃勃  令人興奮」這樣的不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不  應該再具體一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說在體制上可以被承認的像樣點的說法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於全權交與學生負責的學園祭  有些老師也存在著不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖櫻可是歷史悠久  有優良傳統的學園哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在對天宮同學的做法不理解的教師  也並不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下島這個叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為下島老師是反對他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  要想一個讓我們提出他們反對方接受的主題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是那樣的嗎  下島？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧…總之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管那回事  就我剛才說的主題是絕對需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們自己也要給自己定個指標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借這個機會認真的考慮一下也並不壞  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天宮出院後開始算起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…給你們一個星期時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這差不多能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…下島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人討論不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…學美…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學美回來之前  我們兩個人開始考慮主題不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老師他畢竟也是老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽取兩個人想出來的主題的話  也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家覺得我們是「隨意想出」的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「隨意想出」的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是兩個人嘗試想出的主題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小芽兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的…所以才說是「隨意想出」的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說哪一個作為主題都不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼會這樣欠缺靈感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概  這些都太追求華麗反而過於籠統了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法令人覺得「生機勃勃  令人興奮」了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話在比賽中可是贏不了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩三圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出氣勢來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感…感覺好像要想出甚麼來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  再跑一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT ON  FIGHT ON…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是…按照我們自己的方法來考慮吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊…贊成…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咽下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能忍住不吐出來真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（學美出院日！）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:20.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（風格與用語要統一  避開抽象以及曖昧的表現）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:38.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天要定下來！）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子…餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼亂來的話飯會燒糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣才不會燒糊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好飽好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給家裡打個電話說一聲行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡的人不擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣躺著的話  就能更好地看星星了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天宮學美  出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽同學說你們在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個文件是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱著我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小芽成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  又似乎成為了親密的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過學園祭  應該會和更多的人結成伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是那麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:39.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（從朋友到伙伴）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六話  『桂糖甜甜圈·幸福』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:47.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：シュガーレイズド是某家專門生產甜甜圈的公司的產品名）
